# Redirect the bare domain straight to the ventures hub at the server level
# (HTTP redirect, before any page renders) instead of the old client-side
# meta-refresh in index.html, which showed a visible white "Redirecting…"
# flash. ^/$ matches only the exact root path -- everything else
# (mishra-ventures/live-market/, etc.) is left untouched.
RedirectMatch 301 ^/$ /mishra-ventures/
